<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        header nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 0.5rem;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .hero button {
            background: #ff6347;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .hero button:hover {
            background: #ff4500;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .feature {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 300px;
        }
        .feature img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
        }
        .feature h3 {
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<div class="hero" id="home">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Landing Page</h1>
    <p>Discover amazing features and benefits.</p>
    <button>Get Started</button>
</div>

<section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="feature">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Feature 1">
        <h3>Feature One</h3>
        <p>Explore the amazing feature one that makes everything easier and faster.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Feature 2">
        <h3>Feature Two</h3>
        <p>Discover the power of feature two that brings efficiency to your workflow.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Feature 3">
        <h3>Feature Three</h3>
        <p>Experience the simplicity and elegance of feature three in your projects.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Landing Page. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
